                  <additions ana="medium">
                     <p>Occasional marginal emendations.</p> 
                       <p>Leaf added by AM reads: <q>
                        Ur Elis sögu.
                        Framan af Þorsteins sögu Vikings<ex>sonar</ex>.
                        Frä Magnuse i Brædratungu.
                        Ur Adonias sögu.
                        Framan af Remundar sögu.
                        Fra nefndum Magnuse.
                        Her eru og ur Hektors sögu 2. blöd.</q>
                        Another added note in AM's hand reads: <q>þesse 2. blöd ur Þorsteins sögu hefi eg f<ex>ei</ex>nged an<ex>n</ex>arsstadar</q>.
                        </p>
